Pre-Game Insights: A Malian refereeing quartet, led by central referee Boubou Traore, has arrived in Garoua to officiate the crucial Cameroon vs Namibia AFCON qualifier on September 7, 2024.
The referees include assistant referees Modibo Samake and Amadou Belly Guisse, as well as fourth official Sory Ibrahima. They arrived on September 4, 2024, and will commence training on September 5.
